WEBVTT

00:04:29.436 --> 00:04:33.529
And then all of a sudden, magically,
the bikes fly up in the air,

00:04:33.553 --> 00:04:35.092
over the clouds,

00:04:35.116 --> 00:04:36.304
over the moon,

00:04:36.328 --> 00:04:38.619
and they're going to save "E.T."

00:04:39.394 --> 00:04:41.672
So I turn to see my children's faces,

00:04:41.696 --> 00:04:46.166
and Robby is enraptured,
he's there with them, he's saving E.T.,

00:04:46.190 --> 00:04:48.046
he's a happy boy.

00:04:48.070 --> 00:04:51.208
And I turn to Caroline,
and she's crying her eyes out.

00:04:51.866 --> 00:04:53.411
And I said, "What's the matter?"

00:04:53.435 --> 00:04:58.970
And she said, "Why can't I save E.T.?
Why can't I come?"

